Papercutcraft.name: Papercutcraft

kurzgesagt.name: kurzgesagt
kurzgesagt.description: A DreamBooth finetune of Stable Diffusion v1.5 model trained on a bunch of stills from Kurzgesagt videos

Dreamlike Diffusion.name: Dreamlike Diffusion
Dreamlike Diffusion.description: Dreamlike Diffusion 1.0 is SD 1.5 fine tuned on high quality art, made by dreamlike.art

Analog Diffusion.name: Analog Diffusion
Analog Diffusion.description: A dreambooth model trained on a diverse set of analog photographs

Funko Diffusion.name: Funko Diffusion
Funko Diffusion.description: Stable Diffusion fine tuned on Funko Pop, by PromptHero.

Double Exposure Diffusion.name: Double Exposure Diffusion
Double Exposure Diffusion.description: The Double Exposure Diffusion model, trained specifically on images of people and a few animals

Microscopic.name: Microscopic
Microscopic.description: This is the fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model trained on microscopic images

Balloon Art.name: Balloon Art
Balloon Art.description: This is the fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model trained on Twisted Balloon images

Future Diffusion.name: Future Diffusion
Future Diffusion.description: This creates high quality 3D images with a futuristic Sci-Fi theme

Seek.art MEGA.name: Seek.art MEGA
Seek.art MEGA.description: Seek.art MEGA is a general use 'anything' model that significantly improves on 1.5 across dozens of styles. Created by Coreco at seek.art

Valorant Diffusion.name: Valorant Diffusion
Valorant Diffusion.description: This model was trained on the Valorant agents splash arts, and some extra arts on the official website

Hassanblend.name: Hassanblend
Hassanblend.description: This model was for creating people

ACertainThing.name: ACertainThing
ACertainThing.description: An improved version of Anything v3 made with ACertainThing, focusing on scenes rather than characters

GTA5 Artwork Diffusion.name: GTA5 Artwork Diffusion
GTA5 Artwork Diffusion.description: This model was trained on the loading screens, gta storymode, and gta online DLCs artworks. Which includes characters, background, chop, and some objects. The model can do people and portrait pretty easily, as well as cars, and houses. For some reasons, the model stills automatically include in some game footage, so landscapes tend to look a bit more game-like.

Trinart Characters.name: Trinart Characters
Trinart Characters.description: Derrida (formerly TrinArt Characters v2) is a stable diffusion v1-based model that was further improved on the previous characters v1 model. While this is still a versatility and compositional variation anime/manga model like other TrinArt models, when compared to the v1 model, Derrida was focused on more anatomical stability and slightly less on variation due to further multi-epoch training and finetuning.

Smoke Diffusion.name: Smoke Diffusion
Smoke Diffusion.description: This is the fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model trained on images of smoke

Supermarionation.name: Supermarionation
Supermarionation.description: This is a fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model (based on v1.5) trained on screenshots from Gerry Anderson Supermarionation stop motion animation movie, basically from Thunderbirds tv series

Dreamlike Photoreal.name: Dreamlike Photoreal
Dreamlike Photoreal.description: Dreamlike Photoreal 1.0 is a photorealistic Stable Diffusion 1.5 model fine tuned on high quality photos, made by dreamlike.art.

PortraitPlus.name: PortraitPlus
PortraitPlus.description: This is a dreambooth model trained on a diverse set of close to medium range portraits of people.

Vintedois Diffusion.name: Vintedois Diffusion
Vintedois Diffusion.description: Vintedois (22h) Diffusion model trained by Predogl and piEsposito with open weights, configs and prompts (as it should be).  This model was trained on a large amount of high quality images with simple prompts to generate beautiful images without a lot of prompt engineering.

Darkest Diffusion.name: Darkest Diffusion
Darkest Diffusion.description: A free and open source Stable Diffusion model created by AI-Characters, trained on the artstyle of the game 'Darkest Dungeon'

Min Illust Background.name: Min Illust Background
Min Illust Background.description: This fine-tuned Stable Diffusion v1.5 model was trained on a selection of artistic works by Sin Jong Hun

Dark Victorian Diffusion.name: Dark Victorian Diffusion
Dark Victorian Diffusion.description: finetuned on dark, moody, victorian imagery

DnD Item.name: DnD Item
DnD Item.description: This is a model (dnditem) for creating magic items, for the game Dungeons and Dragons! It was trained to be very similar to the official results that are available here: https://www.dndbeyond.com/magic-items

ModernArt Diffusion.name: ModernArt Diffusion
ModernArt Diffusion.description: You can use this model to generate modernart style images

HASDX.name: HASDX
HASDX.description: He merged a few checkpoints and got something buttery and amazing. Does great with things other then people too. It can do anything really. It doesn't need crazy prompts either. Keep it simple. No need for all the artist names and trending on whatever.

Liberty.name: Liberty
Liberty.description: A merge with over 23 other models with a methodical, careful and genuine approach. Freedom of prompting art or photo or both, landscapes or backgrounds or interiors, people or entities or scenes, stiff poses or movement or even mouth and facial emotions.

3DKX.name: 3DKX
3DKX.description: SFW model with limited nsfw capabilities (suggestive nsfw) that is highly versatile for 3D renders.

Moedel.name: Moedel
Moedel.description: Moe.del produces cute female characters. It is also a mix of Stable Diffusion 1.4/1.5 in different proportions so you can challenge it to generate for you pretty much anything using regular SD prompts (like cute dogs, cats etc.)

DreamLikeSamKuvshinov.name: DreamLikeSamKuvshinov
DreamLikeSamKuvshinov.description: A mixture of Dreamlike Diffusion 1.0, SamDoesArt V3 and Kuvshinov style models.  Created mostly for exploring different character concepts with a focus on drawings, but the mix happened to be pretty good at realistic-ish images, all thanks to wonderful models that it uses.

Sygil-Dev Diffusion.name: Sygil-Dev Diffusion
Sygil-Dev Diffusion.description: This model is a Stable Diffusion v1.5 fine-tune trained on the Imaginary Network Expanded Dataset. It is an advanced version of Stable Diffusion and can generate nearly all kinds of images, no matter humans, reflections, cities, architecture, fantasy, digital arts, landscapes, or nature views.

Healy's Anime Blend.name: Healy's Anime Blend
Healy's Anime Blend.description: This is a blend of some anime models mixed with 'realistic' stuff

GuFeng.name: GuFeng
GuFeng.description: This is a model of ancient Chinese style, and it also belongs to the model series with ink and water orientation

Elldreth's Lucid Mix.name: Elldreth's Lucid Mix
Elldreth's Lucid Mix.description: It's an all-around easy-to-prompt general purpose semi-realistic to realistic model that cranks out some really nice images. No trigger words required

Sci-Fi Diffusion.name: Sci-Fi Diffusion
Sci-Fi Diffusion.description: A Sci-Fi themed model trained on SD 1.5 with a 26K+ image dataset

Ultraskin.name: Ultraskin
Ultraskin.description: This model will add a LOT of skin detail compared to SD 2.1. Sometimes this makes images look more realistic, sometimes less realistic!

Sonic Diffusion.name: Sonic Diffusion
Sonic Diffusion.description: SonicDiffusionV2.ckpt was trained on AnythingV3 for 200 epochs of 203 hand captioned Sonic images from various artists

PPP.name: PPP
PPP.description: PPP is a realistic model merge, tested and tweaked for human females. Mostly based on NSFW models

Anygen.name: Anygen
Anygen.description: A best of both worlds - merging the anime of Anything v3 with Protogens photorealism - VAE is included

Protogen Infinity.name: Protogen Infinity
Protogen Infinity.description: Protogens photorealism mixed with more science fiction, comic, and synthwave to make ultimate awesomeness

Dreamshaper.name: Dreamshaper
Dreamshaper.description: Merged model mix of Midnight mixer, roboEtics, f222, elldrethSLucidMix, Seek.ART Mega, rpg, hassanBlend, modelshoot and roboDiffusion

Zelda BOTW.name: Zelda BOTW
Zelda BOTW.description: based off work of great artworks from Legend of Zelda: Breath of The Wild

Marvel Diffusion.name: Marvel Diffusion
Marvel Diffusion.description: This model was trained on images from the animated Marvel Disney+ show What If, which includes characters, background, and some objects

T-Shirt Diffusion.name: T-Shirt Diffusion
T-Shirt Diffusion.description: Generates t-shirt logos, base model is vintedois-diffusion with additional training on t-shirt logos size 640x640px
trigger: as a t-shirt logo in the style of <MAGIFACTORY> art

Lawlas's yiff mix.name: Lawlas's yiff mix
Lawlas's yiff mix.description: Based on yiffy-e18 and Anything, produces sfw/nsfw furry anthro artworks of different styles with consistant quality, while maintaining details on stuff like clothes, background, etc. with simpler prompts.

DGSpitzer Art Diffusion.name: DGSpitzer Art Diffusion
DGSpitzer Art Diffusion.description: Dreambooth model based on Vintedois, trained on a dataset of DGSpitzer art. Styles included are outline, sketch, anime, painting and landscape

Dan Mumford Style.name: Dan Mumford Style
Dan Mumford Style.description: Model trained with a dataset of DanMumford Style images, courtesy of Flonix
trigger: in the style of dan mumford

PFG.name: PFG
PFG.description: NSFW Model for realistic and Hentai images

Epic Diffusion.name: Epic Diffusion
Epic Diffusion.description: Epic Diffusion is a general purpose model based on Stable Diffusion 1.x intended to replace the official SD releases as your default model. It is focused on providing high quality output in a wide range of different styles, with support for NFSW content.

Deliberate.name: Deliberate
Deliberate.description: This model provides you the ability to create anything you want. The more power of prompt knowledges you have, the better results you'll get. It basically means that you'll never get a perfect result with just a few words. You have to fill out your prompt line extremely detailed

Edge Of Realism.name: Edge Of Realism
Edge Of Realism.description: A spin off from Level4. Built to produce high quality photos. Sometimes photos will come out as uncanny as they are on the edge of realism.

Concept Sheet.name: Concept Sheet
Concept Sheet.description: This model is just the first dreambooth iteration for concept-sheet/old-books style. Based on SD 2.1

CharHelper.name: CharHelper
CharHelper.description: This model was trained on a digital painting style mainly with characters and portraits. The main objective is to train a model to be a tool to help with character design ideas

Pokemon3D.name: Pokemon3D
Pokemon3D.description: This model was trained on Gen 1-8 Pokemon low poly renders

pix2pix.name: pix2pix
pix2pix.description: Model specifically trained for pix2pix use

Vivid Watercolors.name: Vivid Watercolors
Vivid Watercolors.description: The model is trained with beautiful, artist-agnostic watercolor images using the midjourney method

Counterfeit.name: Counterfeit
Counterfeit.description: Counterfeit is anime style Stable Diffusion model

Openniji.name: Openniji
Openniji.description: The Stable Diffusion model trained on Nijijourney images

Pastel Mix.name: Pastel Mix
Pastel Mix.description: The model is trained with beautiful, artist-agnostic watercolor images using the midjourney method

Pulp Vector Art.name: Pulp Vector Art
Pulp Vector Art.description: Style model for Stable Diffusion mimicking vector style. vector-art and pulp model mix

Rainbowpatch.name: Rainbowpatch
Rainbowpatch.description: Rainbowpatch is a fine-tuned model specifically trained to generate high-quality stylized images, this model doesn't require complicated detailed text prompts.

Vector Art.name: Vector Art
Vector Art.description: This is a style model for Stable Diffusion 2.1 mimicking vector style.

T-Shirt Print Designs.name: T-Shirt Print Designs
T-Shirt Print Designs.description: This is a style model for creating prints for tshirts

GorynichMix.name: GorynichMix
GorynichMix.description: Model mix based on any4.5, Elysium, Dreamlike and few more models

Cheese Daddys Landscape Mix.name: Cheese Daddys Landscape Mix
Cheese Daddys Landscape Mix.description: This model is tweak and more merges mainly intended for landscapes, but works decent for people

Rachel Walker Watercolors.name: Rachel Walker Watercolors
Rachel Walker Watercolors.description: This checkpoint is trained on the art of Rachel Walker, a New Zealand artist who paints beautiful watercolors.

Project Unreal Engine 5.name: Project Unreal Engine 5
Project Unreal Engine 5.description: This checkpoint is trained to look like Unreal Engine 5 renders

Unstable Ink Dream.name: Unstable Ink Dream
Unstable Ink Dream.description: Create a variety of styles including realistic photos, realistic drawings, and animations like last three fig

PRMJ.name: PRMJ
PRMJ.description: Custom built SD2.1 generalist model from 28k SFW images

Elldreths Retro Mix.name: Elldreths Retro Mix
Elldreths Retro Mix.description: A retro twist on Elldreths other models

VinteProtogenMix.name: VinteProtogenMix
VinteProtogenMix.description: A beautiful blend of Vintedois and an early Protogen model to create fantabulous images

Rodent Diffusion.name: Rodent Diffusion
Rodent Diffusion.description: A model created by Youtuber 'Nerdy Rodent' for creating great images with almost any prompt

Anything v3.name: Anything v3
Anything v3.description: The original horde Anything model with the VAE built in

Woop-Woop Photo.name: Woop-Woop Photo
Woop-Woop Photo.description: A model trained to make detailed, anatomically-accurate (hands, faces, genitals, etc) illustrations of humans and non-humans alike

Abyss OrangeMix.name: Abyss OrangeMix
Abyss OrangeMix.description: A model trained to create CG anime characters

Microcasing.name: Microcasing
Microcasing.description: A cross of knollingcase and microworlds, for creating tiny worlds in a case

ChilloutMix.name: ChilloutMix
ChilloutMix.description: For creating images of nude solo women

Microchars.name: Microchars
Microchars.description: A cross of Cute Rich Style and microworlds, for creating tiny 3d figurines

Microcritters.name: Microcritters
Microcritters.description: A cross of Jak's Creepy Critter and microworlds, for creating tiny 3d monsters

AbyssOrangeMix-AfterDark.name: AbyssOrangeMix-AfterDark
AbyssOrangeMix-AfterDark.description: AbyssOrangeMix trained for creating NSFW images

Grapefruit Hentai.name: Grapefruit Hentai
Grapefruit Hentai.description: Grapefruit aims to be a hentai model with a bright and more softer anime style.

Experience.name: Experience
Experience.description: A generalist model with a slight leaning towards science-fiction and 3d renders

Kenshi.name: Kenshi
Kenshi.description: An anime-style model merge that included Nixeu, WLOP, Guweiz, BoChen, and many others

DucHaiten Classic Anime.name: DucHaiten Classic Anime
DucHaiten Classic Anime.description: DucHaiten's classic anime charecter model, similar to 80's/90's artwork

Rev Animated.name: Rev Animated
Rev Animated.description: This model is mainly intended for Portraits and Full Body Anime-like pictures. Fantasy landscapes are decent.

526Mix-Animated.name: 526Mix-Animated
526Mix-Animated.description: The goal of this model was to anchor 526Mix's whimsical and artistic personality into anime. 526Mix can do a pretty cool anime style (and other 2D styles), but it can be a bit unreliable at times. This simple mix increases the reliability, depth, and nuance in 526Mix's anime and anime-esque capabilities.

A to Zovya RPG.name: A to Zovya RPG
A to Zovya RPG.description: encompass all things RPG Fantasy Art generation related. From landscapes, ruins, castles to characters and monster concepts

Colorful.name: Colorful
Colorful.description: Realistic fantasy portraits, landscapes with vibrant colors, slightly photorealistic

Movie Diffusion.name: Movie Diffusion
Movie Diffusion.description: Movie Diffusion is SD 1.5 trained on 35mm film stills from popular movies.

GuoFeng.name: GuoFeng
GuoFeng.description: This is a Chinese gorgeous antique style model, which can also be said to be an antique game character model with a 2.5D texture

Anime Pencil Diffusion.name: Anime Pencil Diffusion
Anime Pencil Diffusion.description: A dreambooth finetune of stable diffusion 1.5 model that will output stuff in anime pencil concept drawing style.

BPModel.name: BPModel
BPModel.description: Anime model similar to A Certain Thing, but custom trained on 1024x1024 resolution images

UMI Olympus.name: UMI Olympus
UMI Olympus.description: A model that generates extremely high quality landscapes, space battles, and fantasy settings. It can also generate very high quality anime characters, though that is not its primary purpose

Uhmami.name: Uhmami
Uhmami.description: a blend of anime-focused models with a semi-realistic aesthetic, combining 3D digital imagery with photography. It allows the use of prompts based on booru tags, similar to the novelai model, resulting in high-quality semi-realistic images

Neurogen.name: Neurogen
Neurogen.description: This model gives a very good detail of skin and textures. Great for close-up photorealistic portraits as well as various characters and models.

NeverEnding Dream.name: NeverEnding Dream
NeverEnding Dream.description: This is a dream that you will never want to wake up from. A NeverEnding Dream.  Similar to Dreamshaper, but able to use danbooru tags

Protogen Anime.name: Protogen Anime
Protogen Anime.description: A cocktail mix of a bit of everything

SynthwavePunk.name: SynthwavePunk
SynthwavePunk.description: A mix of synthwave and inkpunk

Graphic-Art.name: Graphic-Art
Graphic-Art.description: Style model for Stable Diffusion. Mainly focusing on graphic design.

Illuminati Diffusion.name: Illuminati Diffusion
Illuminati Diffusion.description: Illuminati Diffusion is a latent text-to-image diffusion model that has been conditioned on high aesthetic synthetic images through fine-tuning. It was trained on 82,000 images locally with a single 3090ti, taking over 100 hours.

SD-Silicon.name: SD-Silicon
SD-Silicon.description: SD-Silicon: A series of general-purpose models based off the experimental automerger, autoMBW.

FKing SciFi.name: FKing SciFi
FKing SciFi.description: Trained on 666 images, hand captioned, general, but limited sci-fi model. It has been trained on armour concepts, futuristic backgrounds, androids and robots, as well as some fantasy stuff, like werecreatures.

RealBiter.name: RealBiter
RealBiter.description: This blend model aims to achieve versatility in generating images that are almost realistic but with a touch of fantasy and a polished aesthetic. It performs well with both illustrations and simulated photographs, but it particularly excels with the latter

FaeTastic.name: FaeTastic
FaeTastic.description: A beautiful mixed model (22 mixes) including Noise Offset to create a wide-range of images

OrbAI.name: OrbAI
OrbAI.description: This model gives you the possibilty to have an orb and put awesome stuff inside of it like animals, universe, solarsystems, fractal images whatever you can think of

Realism Engine.name: Realism Engine
Realism Engine.description: This new model was fine-tuned using a vast collection of public domain images, ensuring that it can generate images across a wide range of contexts. While it may not be as strong in generating abstract or highly stylized images, it excels in generating images that are true to life, visually compelling and that accurately reflect the input textual description

Jim Eidomode.name: Jim Eidomode
Jim Eidomode.description: I have created something amazing that creates very stylized images, especially digital art. The model is good at creating animals, women, men, fantastic landscapes and much more.

Dungeons n Waifus.name: Dungeons n Waifus
Dungeons n Waifus.description: A handpicked and curated merge of the best of the best in fantasy world, character & creature design. Should serve as a bit of a swiss army knife / multi-tool to create any and all fantasy art, character concepts, portraits, designs, locations, & even a bit of n00ds

TrexMix.name: TrexMix
TrexMix.description: This is an anime-centric model. It is a massive merge (20+ models) of SD 1.4 and 1.5-based checkpoints. The intent behind this model is to provide good anatomy, realistic lighting and extremely beautiful backgrounds

ExpMix Line.name: ExpMix Line
ExpMix Line.description: Realistic anime styled drawings with extra emphasis on outlines

Disco Elysium.name: Disco Elysium
Disco Elysium.description: Trained on the character portraits from the game Disco Elysium. Can also do great backgrounds, able to be used without a trigger

Something.name: Something
Something.description: A lot of things are being discovered lately, such as a way to merge model using mbw automatically, offset noise to get much darker result, and even VAE tuning. This anime model is intended to use all of those features as the improvements

RCNZ Dumb Monkey.name: RCNZ Dumb Monkey
RCNZ Dumb Monkey.description: They let the monkey loose at the 'Merge Model' tab, and smashed models together and this awesome generalist model came out!

PIXHELL.name: PIXHELL
PIXHELL.description: The model recreates Pixelart style but with more modern take on the 8bit style. This model is great for side scroller environments but it works great for characters when using controlnet for 2.1 for openpose and also it's great for props and other things

Korestyle.name: Korestyle
Korestyle.description: A model for semi-realistic comic book style sketches

PVC.name: PVC
PVC.description: This model is a latent diffusion model finetuned on Waifu Diffusion v1.5 beta 2 with PVC figure images. You can use Danbooru tags to generate images

Aurora.name: Aurora
Aurora.description: Aurora is a Stable Diffusion model, similar to its predecessor Kenshi, with the goal of capturing my own feelings towards the anime styles I desire.The name Aurora, which means 'dawn' in Latin, represents the idea of a new beginning and a fresh start.

Char.name: Char
Char.description: A 1024 res SD v1.5 trained (not merged) resolution model for various high-quality artstyles. NOTE: There are 42 different possible triggers depending on what you want to create, please see the homepage for the full list

Perfect World.name: Perfect World
Perfect World.description: The pursuit of perfect balance between realism and anime, a semi-realistic model aimed to achieve beautiful realistic faces with sexy hentai bodies.

JoMad Diffusion.name: JoMad Diffusion
JoMad Diffusion.description: SD 1.5 model trained on a sample of Joe Madureiras artwork, this model was combined with another anime style model to create the blend uploaded here.

RCNZ Gorilla With A Brick.name: RCNZ Gorilla With A Brick
RCNZ Gorilla With A Brick.description: This time its a Gorilla at the 'Merge Model' tab, and smashed photorealism models together and this awesome generalist model came out!

Ether Real Mix.name: Ether Real Mix
Ether Real Mix.description: Ether Real Mix is a realistic to semi-realistic anime style model tuned with the flexibility for general purpose use (hopefully). It still has some shortcomings inherit to anime models such as biases in generating females and humans.

Lyriel.name: Lyriel
Lyriel.description: This model is generally designed for portraits and full-length anime style photos. Fantastic landscapes are quite decent. And it doesn't require kilometer-long queries to get a high-quality result.

DnD Map Generator.name: DnD Map Generator
DnD Map Generator.description: This model is trained on various D&D Battlemaps. Use the negative prompt: 'grid' to improve some maps, or use the gridless version. Try to experiment with the CFG scale, 10 can create some amazing results but to each their own.

Beautiful Realistic Asians.name: Beautiful Realistic Asians
Beautiful Realistic Asians.description: Trained on countless pictures of Beautiful Asian women. (some nsfw images included)
